#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:4
#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:11
msgid "CSS Guidelines"
msgstr "CSS 安全規範"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:14
msgid "To ensure your Custom Pages integrate seamlessly with the NetBox UI and prevent breaking other users' viewing experiences, please strictly follow these CSS guidelines."
msgstr "為了確保您的自定義頁面完美融合進系統，且不破壞其他人的瀏覽體驗，請嚴格遵守以下安全規範。"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:17
msgid "Core Principle: No Global CSS Pollution"
msgstr "核心原則：禁止全域污染"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:18
msgid "Your page code is directly embedded into the NetBox framework. Any CSS rules without a scoped boundary will leak out and break the official NetBox menus and layout."
msgstr "您的程式碼是被直接嵌入入 NetBox 原生框架中的。任何沒有邊界限制的 CSS 都會向外滲漏，並癱瘓 NetBox 原本的系統版面。"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:21
msgid "Incorrect (Do Not Use)"
msgstr "錯誤寫法 (絕對禁止使用)"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:22
msgid "Never write global styles targeting raw HTML elements like below:"
msgstr "絕不可以直接撰寫針對全域核心標籤的樣式，例如："

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:24
msgid "This sets the entire NetBox background to black, causing a disaster!"
msgstr "這將會把整個大系統的背景變成黑色的，導致全站版面大災難！"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:33
msgid "Best Practice 1: Inline Styles"
msgstr "最佳實踐一：行內樣式"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:34
msgid "Writing styles directly on elements is the safest and will not cause pollution:"
msgstr "直接把樣式寫在網頁 HTML 元素屬性上是最安全的："

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:36
msgid "Safe web content"
msgstr "安全範圍內的網頁內容"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:39
msgid "Best Practice 2: Scoped Wrapper"
msgstr "最佳實踐二：邊界坎套"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:40
msgid "If you must use a <style> block, create a unique outer wrapper ID or class, and nest all your CSS under it:"
msgstr "如果您堅持要寫整坨的 <style> 樣式表，請一定要使用一個獨有的 ID 或 Class 容器把它們包起來："

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:42
msgid "This only affects the inner p tag of your custom container."
msgstr "這將只會影響這個坎套以內的標籤。"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:49
msgid "Ensure all your content is wrapped safely."
msgstr "確保您所有的內容都只在範圍內。"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:51
msgid "Safe custom content here"
msgstr "在這之中編輯您的安全內容"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:54
msgid "Ultimate Practice: Bootstrap 5"
msgstr "最高實踐：使用原生 Bootstrap 5"

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:55
msgid "NetBox natively includes Bootstrap 5. We highly recommend using native Bootstrap classes for formatting. You might not need custom CSS at all:"
msgstr "系統內建了 Bootstrap 5，我們強烈建議您直接使用原生的 Bootstrap 介面設計類別進行排版，這樣您根本不用寫自己的 CSS："

#: templates/netbox_custom_pages/docs/css_policy.html:56
msgid "Use Bootstrap cards, buttons, and spacing."
msgstr "盡情使用 Bootstrap 的卡片元件、按鈕、陰影與間距排版"

